user.biography: The official Instagram account of Counter-Strike: Global Offensive, available on Steam.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CS:GO on September 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text: Today we are shipping the 2021 Community Sticker Capsule, featuring 21 unique stickers from various Community Workshop artists. Get yours in-game now! #CSGO

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CS:GO on August 12, 2021. May be a cartoon of book and text.

node.text: Today we’re releasing the Tacticians Music Kit box featuring six new music kits. Get yours now in-game! #CSGO

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CS:GO on May 03, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
Today Operation Broken Fang has officially ended. 

As part of today’s update we are removing Train from Active Duty and replacing it with Ancient, which has received numerous changes to A site and minor adjustments to B site. 

We’re also shipping the Snakebite Case, introducing CS:GO 360 Stats, and adding new chickens. Check all of this out now in-game! #CSGO

node.text:
Today we are opening up Broken Fang Premier to everyone. Premier, which introduces a pick/ban phase to the start of a competitive match, allows players to test their mettle across the entire Active Duty map pool. Pick and ban maps, choose your starting side, and work together to win 16 rounds. 

Operation Pass holders and Prime accounts are in one pool of players who play with and against each other in Premier. Accounts that are neither Prime, nor have an Operation Pass, are in a separate Premier pool. #CSGO

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CS:GO on March 18, 2021. May be a cartoon.

node.text: Today we’re shipping the Poorly Drawn Sticker Capsule and three new Music Kits; the Hades Music Kit from @supergiantgames, the Lowlife Pack from @neckdeepuk, and the CHAIN$AW.LXADXUT. Music Kit from @scarlxrd. These are all available now in-game! #CSGO

node.text: Today we are shipping 2020 RMR team stickers, available now in Legends, Contenders, and Challengers capsules. These are available now in-game! #CSGO

node.text: Introducing CS:GO’s 10th Operation, Operation Broken Fang. Featuring new game modes, agents, weapon collections, stickers, and more—available now! #CSGO

node.text: Today we are shipping the Fracture Case, featuring weapon finishes from more than 17 Community artists. Get yours now in-game as a post match reward or from the Steam Community Market! #CSGO

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CS:GO on July 23, 2020.

node.text: Today we are adding Mutiny and Swamp and removing Chlorine and Jungle from official matchmaking. These new maps are playable now! #CSGO
